 View, which is consistent\nwith the ratio of CBMG and GDMG. Now 511keV gammas GDMG are preliminarily\ndetected with ~5 and >10 sigma respectively around Galactic Centre. Also we\nhave obtained near 105events of CBMG in with quite low background of only a few\n10% in total CBMG events. Thus we obtained good data for both with high\nstatistics and very low systematics even one day observation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2020 05:52:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
