r bounds to show that the above\nalgorithms are tight up to factors of $\\log n$. Additionally, we provide\nalgorithms for realizing trees and an $\\tilde{O}(1)$ round algorithm for\napproximate degree sequence realization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2020 07:36:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 17:49:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 15:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-19"}
