ents for the dielectric and\nmetallic nanoparticle arrays. The electric fields are enhanced by a factor of\n1200 and 400, close to the particles for gold and amorphous silicon,\nrespectively, and the modes extend over half a micron around the particles for\nboth materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2020 15:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-14"}
